      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm 22 weeks pregnant and my sinuses are killing me. like, everything is so stuffed up i can barely breathe or sleep. i really need something that works fast so i can actually rest, can i take some Sudafed or is that gonna be an issue? also i have some ciprofloxacin left over from a previous infection, would that be okay to finish up or should i avoid it?",
